What is a Russian Manicure?
A Russian manicure, also known as a dry manicure, is a meticulous nail treatment that involves using an electronic file to gently exfoliate and shape the nails. Unlike traditional manicures, which may use water to soak the nails, a Russian manicure focuses on precision and cleanliness, offering a longer-lasting and flawless finish. This technique is perfect for achieving the ideal base for stunning nail art in Dubai.

